Cooper Square (under the Third Avenue Elevated) at E. 5th Street and showing at the N.E. corner a gasoline station occupying the site long held by a 4 story frame house, No. 25 Cooper Square. Tenements seen at the right are No's. 207 to 211 E. 5th Street.

March 24, 1938.
